## **4. Step-by-Step: GitHub par Kaise Dalein?**

1.  GitHub par **New Repository** banayein.
2.  Name rakhein `VulnReport-Pro`.
3.  **Public** select karein.
4.  "Add a README file" ko **Uncheck** rehne dein (kyunka hum apna README dalenge).
5.  Repo banne ke baad, apne computer par ye commands chalayein:
    ```bash
    git init
    git add .
    git commit -m "Initial release of VulnReport Pro ✨"
    git branch -M main
    git remote add origin https://github.com/your-username/VulnReport-Pro.git
    git push -u origin main
    ```

